Cisco Command

--------------------------------------------
Switch Configuration L2

!@BASIC SECURITY
line console 0
password cisco
login
exit
line vty 0 15
password cisco
login
exit
service password-encryption

@STEP 1 - Create Voice VLAN
conf t
vlan #
 name VLAn-Name

@Verify
do show vlan brief

@STEP 2 - Assign Ports
@Ito ang unang bagong command.
@Lahat ng phones ay nasa Fa0/1 hanggang Fa0/7.

conf t
interface range #
switchport voice vlan #
spanning-tree portfast

@for verification
show running-config interface fa0/1
show interfaces switchport fa0/1

@Configure Trunk
conf t
interface gi0/1
switchport mode trunk
switchport trunk allowed vlan 200

