Router 2811 Configuration 

@STEP 3 - Create the SVI
 conf t
interface #
no shutdown
exit
interface fa0/0.200
encapsulation dot1Q 200
ip address 172.16.50.1 255.255.255.192

@exclude ip address
conf t
ip dhcp excluded-address 172.16.50.1

@create DHCP POOL
conf t
ip dhcp pool VLAn_name
network 172.16.50.0 255.255.255.192
default-router 172.16.50.1
option 150 ip 172.16.50.1 @// IP address of the CME (Router Subinterface / Default Gateway)

@CME

✅ CME

@Ito na ang bagong topic.
conf t
telephony-service
max-ephones 10
max-dn 10
ip source-address 172.16.50.1 port 2000
auto assign 1 to 7
create cnf-files

✅ Extensions
conf t
ephone-dn 1
 number 1001
@dagdag ng extensions depende sa bilang ng ip phones
@format
ephone-dn #
numer 100#
ephone-dn 7
 number 1007

@ACL
@ACL ay sa Router na natin ilalagay.
